text: Added Shears; Stone Shovel, Pickaxe, Axe, and Sword.
Added Snowballs, Sticks, Dandelion Yellow, Bowls, Sugars, Books, Papers, Coals; Wooden Axe, Shovel, Pickaxe, and Sword.
The texture above aren’t used for anything.
Added Charcoal, Gold Ingot, Iron Ingot, Diamond; Diamond, gold, and iron pickaxe, axe, shovel, sword, Bricks and Clay Ball.
Added Bone Meal, Bows, Flint, String, Feather and Bones.
Added Bed, Flint And Steel, Hoes, some Food-related items and dyes.
Added Melon Seeds,Which Uses the Pumpkin seeds texture.
Added armor, nether bricks, nether Quartz and leather.
Added Bucket, Water Bucket, Lava Bucket, Milk Bucket; Chicken, Cow, Pig and Sheep Spawn Eggs; Eggs and Cakes.
Added Pumpkin Pie, Beetroot Soup, Clock, Minecart, Redstone dust, Rails, Powered Rails, Beetroot Seeds, Beetroot, Carrot, Potatoes, and Baked Potatoes.
Changed the texture for Coal and Charcoal.
Changed the texture for Powered Rail item.
Charcoal now has its own texture.
Added the texture for emeralds,more spawn eggs and slimeballs.
Added Rotten Flesh, Fishing Rod, Raw Fish, Cooked Fish, Raw Salmon, Cooked Salmon, Pufferfish, Clownfish, Magma Cream; Squid, Bat, Cave Spider, Magma Cube, Ghast Spawn Eggs and Boats.

Added Glass Bottles; 12 Potions, 11 Splash Potions; Gold Nugget, Golden Carrot, Nether Wart, Glistering Melon Slice, Golden Apple, Enchanted Golden Apple, Rabbit's Foot, Blaze Rod, Blaze Powder, Ghast Tear, Spider Eye, Fermented Spider Eye, Bottle o' Enchanting, Poisonous Potato, Enchanted Book; Zombie Villager, Ocelot and Blaze Spawn Eggs.
New inventory icons for boats have been added. The sprite now includes paddles and represents their respective wood color.
Added Rabbit Spawn egg, Raw Rabbit, Cooked Rabbit, Rabbit Stew, and Rabbit Hide.
Changed the textures of oak and iron Doors.
Added maps, Witch spawn egg, various versions of Minecarts, Redstone Comparator, Redstone Repeater, Hopper, Cauldron and Item Frames.

Added Raw mutton, Cooked Mutton, Fire Charges; Spawn eggs for Horses, Zombie horse, Skeleton horse, Mule, Donkey, Stray, Husk, and Wither skeleton; Name Tags, Leads, Carrot on a Stick, Tipped Arrows, and Leather Horse Armor.
Added Dragon's Breath, Elytra, End Crystal, Chorus Fruit, Ender Pearl, Eye of Ender,y Popped Chorus Fruit; Spawn Eggs for Shulkers, Endermites, and Polar Bears; and 12 Lingering Potions.
Added Totem of Undying, Explorer Map, Iron Nugget; Spawn Eggs for Llamas, Vindicators, Evokers, and Vexes.
Added Armor Stand, Book and Quill, Firework Star, Firework Rocket, Music Disc;Parrot and Zombie Villager Spawn Egg.
Changeed the texture of Boats,The paddles now represent their respective wood color (except spruce) and the inside rims of the boats are darker.
Added two pre-tinted leaves textures, used for oak and birch leaves blocks when held.
Two textures for pre-tinted spruce leaves have been added. These are similarly used for held items.
A new tinted grass block top texture has been added, for the held grass block.

texts.text: This article is about all changes made to item textures. For the texture atlas that housed all block textures prior to Java Edition 1.5 and Pocket Edition v0.8.0 alpha, see items.png.
In Bedrock Edition, biome-affected items use textures which are already colored, rather than tinting the block texture.
